The '''Panama Davis Cup team''' represents [[Panama]] in [[Davis Cup]] [[tennis]] competition and are governed by the [[Federación Panamena de Tenis]].
Panama currently compete in the Americas Zone of Group III. They have finished 3rd in Group III on two occasions.
==History== Panama competed in its first Davis Cup in [[1996 Davis Cup|1996]].
